### 配置连接
使用环境变量设置了 application.yml，并在 https://supabase.com/ 上创建了一个 PostgreSQL 数据库。
将 application.properties 替换为 application.yml：
```yml
logging:
  file:
    name: app.log
server:
  error:
    include-binding-errors: always
    include-message: always
    include-stacktrace: on_param
  port: ${SERVER_PORT:8080}
spring:
  datasource:
    username: ${DATASOURCE_USERNAME:sa}
    password: ${DATASOURCE_PASSWORD:''}
    url: ${DATASOURCE_URL:jdbc:h2:mem:testdb}
    driver-class-name: ${DATASOURCE_DRIVER_CLASS_NAME:org.h2.Driver}
  jpa:
    database: ${JPA_DATABASE:h2}
    hibernate:
      ddl-auto: update
    properties:
      hibernate:
        jdbc:
          lob:
            non_contextual_creation: true
    show-sql: true
```
